How to start the program:

Start 3 servers
start a server by navigating to server and running:
    go run main.go <id> <port> <length>

id: the id for this server. should be unique
port: the port that this erver will listen on
The following ports should be used: 5000", 5001", 5002
length: the length of the auction. Amount of bids which can be placed

Satrt clients
start a client by navigating to client and running:
    go run main.go <id>

id: the id for this client. should be unique and not equal to 0
the terminal will prompt you to make bids

The id for a node is used to mkae it's log that it writes to